profile:
Clear Reflections is not your typical window cleaning company.

We have been in operation as a business from 2008 to 2019 as a husband and wife team.
100% satisfaction is the goal for every client we serve.
 We achieve this goal by our communication with our clients and by using above industry standard technics and tools which bring outstanding results.
We take pride in the high quality workmanship that we deliver 
to every customer.
